already on the property

37
00:02:17,131 --> 00:02:18,131
based on
your say-so.

38
00:02:18,131 --> 00:02:19,131
I know, Mr. Dudley.

39
00:02:19,131 --> 00:02:21,131
Honestly, I do.

40
