to have your own
lawyer go over it.

43
00:02:29,130 --> 00:02:31,130
My grandma don’t put
much stock in lawyers.

44
00:02:31,130 --> 00:02:33,130
You’ve been in banking
for a long time now.

45
00:02:33,130 --> 00:02:34,130
If you say
it’s a good deal

46
00:02:34,130 --> 00:02:36,130
we’ll take
your word for it.

