all whipped up.

1761
01:17:48,963 --> 01:17:50,963
I think that’s
what this is.

1762
01:17:53,963 --> 01:17:55,963
Well, that’s different,
all right.

1763
01:17:55,963 --> 01:17:56,963
I could live to be a hundred

1764
01:17:56,963 --> 01:17:58,963
