I really did love the pictures.

1817
01:20:15,957 --> 01:20:18,957
I’m just glad
you’re thinking of me.

1818
01:20:18,957 --> 01:20:20,957
I’ve been thinking
of you, too

1819
01:20:20,957 --> 01:20:22,957
